*Uzmeš* loptu i počneš da igraš. (You take the ball and start to play.)

*Uzmeš* li sladoled? (Will you take the ice cream?)

On *uzme* da radi taj posao. (He takes up the job.)

*Uzmeš* li u obzir sve faktore? (Do you take into account all the factors?)

*Uzmeš* li učešća u tom projektu? (Will you take part in this project?)

Ona je *uzela* da proveri svoje znanje. (She took to test her knowledge.)